task.summary: Transaction details layout rewritten, transactionDetailsActivity modified, Overview supports toolbar guestures
Overview activity replaces main activity, Parts of various layouts moved to get rid of MainActivity debug views
Overview and transaction details activity now have period changing buttons in the toolbar
Settings menu sub activities redesigned completely, Permission callbacks supported, Tutorial aspects added, Minor text changes
Play store beta second pass (Lint > Performance Next)
Play store beta third pass, Database operations now Asynchronous

Ver 1.0.2 ALPHA 2016-09-08 *[BUGFIX] Profiles/Categories edited when the user indicated they were making a new one *[ADD] Override end date button, profiles automatically change start date to the precision level of the period. (IE: Yearly Period with StartDate set to March 4th 2014 will become StartDate January 1st 2014)

(IE: Yearly Period with StartDate set to March 4th 2014 will become StartDate January 1st 2014)
